OBSERVATIONS:
  Φ₁(2) = 1: trivial
  Φ₂(2) = 3: the cycle generator / simplex factor / Baer partition count
  Φ₃(2) = 7: FORBIDDEN (Fano plane)
  Φ₄(2) = 5: NOT forbidden (achievable)
