          Φ₃(1)=3       Φ₃(2)=7       Φ₃(4)=21
         /    \          |    |         |    \
    Var/μ²  3 Baer   Fano   K₃     PG(2,4)  F₈
    =1/3    planes   plane  poison  Baer    Fibonacci
